        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="常用shell脚本"><a href="#常用shell脚本" class="headerlink" title="常用shell脚本"></a>常用shell脚本</h3><h4 id="VPS工具箱"><a href="#VPS工具箱" class="headerlink" title="VPS工具箱"></a>VPS工具箱</h4><ul><li>设置交换内存，安装宝塔等集合box</li></ul><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget -O box.sh https://raw.githubusercontent.com/BlueSkyXN/SKY-BOX/main/box.sh &amp;&amp; chmod +x box.sh &amp;&amp; clear &amp;&amp; ./box.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
